name: Symmetry
intro: Infrastructure for creating, automating, managing and tracking on-chain funds
introduce: Symmetry is a decentralized crypto indices and actively managed funds infrastructure layer built on Solana, powered by the Symmetry Engine. This innovative on-chain asset management infrastructure covers everything from on-chain funds, indices and multi-token liquidity pools to liquidity routing between indices and DEX aggregators, and public APIs for other DeFi projects to integrate Symmetry products seamlessly.
